Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: No more nukes
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040h3rx
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Oct 1979
Anti-nuclear power protests strengthen in wake of Three Mile Island accident. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less